sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS OAuth
    participant NotebookCtrl as notebook-controller<br/>K8s API
    participant Notebook as Jupyter Workbench<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS OAuth
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KServeCtrl as kserve-controller<br/>K8s API
    participant ModelCtrl as odh-model-controller<br/>K8s API
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant InferenceService as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP mTLS
    participant DSPO as data-science-pipelines-operator<br/>K8s API
    participant DSP as DSP API Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS Bearer
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>Workflow Pods
    participant TrainingOp as training-operator<br/>K8s API
    participant Kueue as kueue<br/>K8s API
    participant TrainingPods as PyTorch Workers<br/>Distributed Training

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Notebook: Workflow 1: Notebook Development
        User->>Dashboard: Login via OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        Dashboard->>NotebookCtrl: Create Notebook CR<br/>K8s API
        NotebookCtrl->>Notebook: Create StatefulSet + Route<br/>K8s API
        User->>Notebook: Develop model<br/>HTTPS OAuth (cookie)
        Notebook->>S3: Save model artifacts<br/>HTTPS (AWS IAM)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over User,InferenceService: Workflow 2: Model Deployment
        User->>Dashboard: Create InferenceService<br/>HTTPS OAuth
        Dashboard->>KServeCtrl: Create InferenceService CR<br/>K8s API
        KServeCtrl->>InferenceService: Create Deployment/KnativeService<br/>K8s API
        KServeCtrl->>ModelCtrl: Notify InferenceService created<br/>Watch
        ModelCtrl->>Istio: Create Route + Gateway + AuthConfig<br/>K8s API
        InferenceService->>S3: Download model<br/>HTTPS (storage-initializer)
        User->>Istio: POST /v2/models/model/infer<br/>Bearer Token
        Istio->>InferenceService: Forward request<br/>mTLS ISTIO_MUTUAL
        InferenceService-->>Istio: Prediction result
        Istio-->>User: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,Argo: Workflow 3: Pipeline Execution
        User->>Dashboard: Create DSPA<br/>HTTPS OAuth
        Dashboard->>DSPO: Create DSPA CR<br/>K8s API
        DSPO->>DSP: Deploy API Server + MariaDB + MinIO<br/>K8s API
        User->>DSP: Submit pipeline (kfp SDK)<br/>HTTPS Bearer Token
        DSP->>Argo: Create Workflow CR<br/>K8s API
        Argo->>S3: Upload/download artifacts<br/>HTTPS
        Argo->>KServeCtrl: Create InferenceService CR<br/>K8s API (pipeline step)
        KServeCtrl->>InferenceService: Deploy model<br/>K8s API
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,TrainingPods: Workflow 4: Distributed Training with Queueing
        User->>TrainingOp: Create PyTorchJob CR<br/>K8s API
        TrainingOp->>Kueue: Create Workload CR<br/>K8s API
        Kueue->>Kueue: Evaluate ClusterQueue quotas<br/>In-process
        Kueue->>TrainingOp: Admit workload<br/>K8s API (patch)
        TrainingOp->>TrainingPods: Create worker pods<br/>K8s API
        TrainingPods->>TrainingPods: Distributed training<br/>TCP (torchrun)
        TrainingPods->>S3: Save checkpoints<br/>HTTPS
        TrainingPods-->>TrainingOp: Training complete<br/>Status update
        TrainingOp->>Kueue: Release quota<br/>Status update
    end
